snippet.title: Ascento Robotics
snippet.description:
The vision of Ascento Robotics is to advance the development of wheeled bipedal robotic
systems, bringing them out of the lab to the real world. Our solution combines the best
of two worlds: It uses the versatility of legs to overcome stairs and obstacles and it uses
its wheels for a fast, energy- and cost-efficient locomotion. This makes our platform the
ideal mobile robot for real-world deployment for many applications.
